## ==========================================
##  1. 项目自定义目录 (Custom Folders)
## ==========================================
# CMake 默认构建目录
/build/
/out/

# vcpkg 相关
vcpkg_cache/
vcpkg_installed/

## ==========================================
##  2. 构建产物 (Build Artifacts)
## ==========================================
*.exe
*.dll
*.lib
*.so
*.dylib
*.pyd

!ThirdParty/DuiLib/lib/*.lib
!ThirdParty/DuiLib/lib/*.pdb

# 临时编译文件
*.obj
*.o
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.exp
*.tlog
*.lastbuildstate
*.recipe
*.ipdb
*.iobj

## ==========================================
##  3. IDE & 编辑器缓存 (IDE & Editors)
## ==========================================
# Visual Studio
.vs/
*.sln.docstates
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.aps
*.ncb
*.opendb
*.opensdf
*.sdf
*.cachefile
*.VC.db

# VS Code
.vscode/
# 如果你想保留 VS Code 的配置（如 launch.json），取消下面注释
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/launch.json

## ==========================================
##  4. CMake 生成的文件 (CMake Internals)
## ==========================================
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
CMakeScripts/
cmake_install.cmake
install_manifest.txt
Makefile
# *.cmake
# 注意：如果你的源码里有自定义 .cmake 文件，请谨慎使用上面那行

## ==========================================
##  5. 临时文件 (Temporary / OS)
## ==========================================
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak
~$*
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db